comments: Harden (LAC) makes contact with Davis' (LAL) right arm, which affects his ability to secure the rebound.
Hachimura (LAL) slightly extends his left hand and marginal brush contact occurs with Theis' (LAC) lower body during the pursuit of the loose ball.
Theis (LAC) gathers the ball and slides out of bounds. Possession is properly awarded to the Lakers.
Powell (LAC) grasps and quickly releases the side of James' (LAL) jersey during the inbound and the contact is marginal.
Davis' (LAL) arm briefly comes around Mann's (LAC) arm as the the two players engage in the paint and the marginal contact quickly dissolves.
Leonard (LAC) and James (LAL) come together during the inbound and marginal contact occurs as Leonard releases away from James.
Leonard's (LAC) off-arm comes out slightly as he ends his drive and the contact with James (LAL) is marginal.
Davis (LAL) moves alongside Leonard (LAC) and avoids making illegal contact with Leonard during his contest of the driving shot attempt.
Davis' (LAL) left arm momentarily comes around Leonard's (LAC) arm as they engage around the perimeter and the marginal contact dissolves shortly thereafter.
Leonard (LAC) moves alongside James' (LAL) path and avoids making illegal contact during his contest of James' driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) grasps and immediately releases Theis' (LAC) right arm as the two players disengage and the contact after the change of possession is marginal.
Mann (LAC) firms up in James' (LAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the screen.
Leonard's (LAC) off-arm comes out slightly as he gathers the ball and marginal brush contact occurs with James (LAL).
James (LAL) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
